phoenix investment adviser llc private company information  bloomberg july    am et capital markets company overview of phoenix investment adviser llc snapshot people company overview phoenix investment adviser llc is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor the firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles it also provides its services to corporations or other businesses the firm invests in fixed income markets it primarily invests in securities and other obligations of companies that are experiencing significant financial or business distress including companies that may be involved in bankruptcy or other reorganization and liquidation proceedings ie distressed and stressed securities primarily corporate bonds the firm employs event driven strategies to make its investments it employs fundamental analysis with focus on bottomup analysis to m phoenix investment adviser llc is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor the firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles it also provides its services to corporations or other businesses the firm invests in fixed income markets it primarily invests in securities and other obligations of companies that are experiencing significant financial or business distress including companies that may be involved in bankruptcy or other reorganization and liquidation proceedings ie distressed and stressed securities primarily corporate bonds the firm employs event driven strategies to make its investments it employs fundamental analysis with focus on bottomup analysis to make its investments the firm obtains external research to complement its inhouse research phoenix investment adviser llc was founded on may   and is based in new york city detailed description the graybar building lexington avenuesuite new york ny united statesfounded in  phone  key executives for phoenix investment adviser llc mr jeffrey lawrence peskind founder chief executive officer chief investment officer senior managing director