kip to content  skip to navigation personal tools search site advanced search… homeabout usour teamnews  publicationscontact us about us info phoenix investment adviser llc is an sec registered investment adviser focusing on high yield credit strategy phoenix was founded by jeffrey l peskind in may  and launched its first strategy in september  this strategy focuses on high yield cash bonds trading at a deep discount to their principal values due to corporate fundamentals or market factorsin january  phoenix launched a lower volatility strategy focusing on credits that are generally in the senior part of the capital structure and generate high current income at the same time the strategy strives to preserve investor capital through extensive hedging during our year history phoenix has grown to manage  billion and currently employs  professionals as of may    process phoenix focuses on high yield debt through deep fundamental analysis and extensive market knowledge our investment team identifies companies that we believe may generate significant capital gains while producing high current income phoenix also looks to capitalize on market inefficiencies where there are vast differences between trading prices and perceived value we strive to uncover opportunities where credits are trading at discounts to our calculation of intrinsic value and we utilize our extensive industry contacts to source securities phoenix analyzes prospects across all industries but focuses on asset rich positive cash flow companies we look throughout the capital structure and across asset classes to identify securities with the greatest perceived return potential for each of our strategies   phoenix investment adviser llc privacy statement terms of use contact us phoenix investment adviser llc company profile  bloomberg feedback phoenix investment adviser llc private company company profile sector financials industry asset management subindustry wealth management phoenix investment adviser llc 